9
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,360
Who would've guessed

10
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:50,000
he'd put his own granddaughter
on the line.

11
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,320
You're silly.

12
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,520
I already talked to my grandpa.

13
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,120
He promised not to
ask about backgrounds.

14
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,000
Just be yourself,

15
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,040
that's enough.

16
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,760
Don't try too hard.

17
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,640
Got it.

18
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,560
I'll quickly review On Writing again,

19
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,120
just in case he quizzes me.

20
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,400
Sounds good.

21
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,640
