23
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,320
On

24
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,320
Writing.

25
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:26,000
[Li Residence]

26
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,000
Hello, Zhijin.

27
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,840
Why am I a little nervous now?

28
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,760
Now that you mention it, me too.

29
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,360
Weren't there supposed to be guests?

30
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,720
Maybe we should wait a bit.

31
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,920
We should go up and say hi first.

32
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,440
Let me take a look at you.

33
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,600
You look great. Let's go.

34
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,920
Hai,

35
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,320
watch your words.

36
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,800
My bad.

37
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,200
We're all on the same side here.

38
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,480
Let's just talk it out.

39
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:13,200
We can work through this.

40
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,920
Grandpa.

41
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,000
Is he...

42
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:26,760
Jiadi.

43
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,040
Zhao.

44
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,480
Grandpa, I'll show Jiadi around first.

45
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,520
Go ahead.

46
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,240
Gentlemen, you all keep chatting.

47
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,680
Zhijin.

48
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,520
Wait up.

49
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,120
Fan.

50
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,800
You just keep watching me all day.

51
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,960
Are you that sure about your judgment?

52
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,280
Maybe you trust yourself too much.

53
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:56,120
Come on, tell me.

54
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,040
Who is he?

55
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,240
Jinghai.

56
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:17,160
What do you mean by that?

57
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:20,200
Finish what you started.

58
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,280
Fine, I'll just say it myself.

59
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,920
Mr. Li.

60
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,120
Nice to meet you.

61
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,960
Didn't expect things
to turn out like this.

62
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,320
My name is Zhao Jiadi.

63
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,000
I'm from Tang City.

64
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,080
I'm Jinhai Zhao Xin's son.

65
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,720
What did you say?

66
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,200
Zhao Xin?

67
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,840
Zhao Xin.

68
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,160
Zhijin.

69
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,680
