76
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
He's not like what you think.

77
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,600
Zhijin,

78
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,960
some people are desperate
to get close to you

79
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:29,840
and to approach the NCC.

80
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,480
Do you know he...

81
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,480
Just keep quiet.

82
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,800
Stop making things worse.

83
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,640
Hey, young man,

84
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,240
let me ask you something.

85
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,520
When you met Liu Xin,

86
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,520
did you know

87
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,880
I'm with the Chamber of Commerce?

88
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,160
Yeah, I knew.

89
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,000
You were running around for me.

90
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,240
When I brought you to dinner,

91
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,480
did you realize

92
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,960
we were competing with Jinhai?

93
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,680
Yes, I knew.

94
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,720
Fan, seriously.

95
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,320
No wonder Zhao Xin

96
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,720
knows so much

97
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,960
about our business secrets?

98
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,120
It's all because of you!

99
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,240
You've been way too careless!

100
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,640
Don't blame Fan for this.

101
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,720
He was tricked by someone shady.

102
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,360
If it were you instead,

103
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,040
the mine would've been taken too.

104
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,000
Stop talking nonsense here!

105
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,960
All of you, quiet!

106
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,080
Fan.

107
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,240
Go on, say it.

108
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,000
You're something else.

109
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,560
Mr. Zhao.

110
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,600
You can't stay here anymore.

111
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,080
Please leave.

112
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,160
Grandpa.

113
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,680
Does his name matter that much?

114
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,400
He's just speaking for himself.

115
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,680
Please don't treat him like this.

116
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,920
Yan, take Zhijin back to her room.

117
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,680
I'm not going.

118
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,880
I'm not going back.

119
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,680
Zhijin.

120
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,480
Mr. Li.

121
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,880
Fan,

122
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,160
I'll say my piece and then leave.

123
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,680
I'm Zhao Xin's son.

124
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,880
I didn't choose

125
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,120
this background.

126
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,120
And I can't run from it either.

127
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,880
Me, Zhao Jiadi,

128
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:40,680
came to Hang City

129
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,960
to start from scratch.

130
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,360
I earned everything

131
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,880
through my own effort.

132
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,920
I never twisted the truth.

133
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,160
I never played both sides.

134
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,440
I've never done anything shady.

135
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,000
And I never wronged anyone.

136
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,160
Scheming and plotting,

137
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,160
that's not who I am.

138
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,440
I don't know

139
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,880
what happened between you and Zhao Xin,

140
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,280
but it's exactly because I don't know

141
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,400
that I couldn't be honest with you.

142
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:30,360
I don't want to feel out of place

143
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,560
because of someone else's burdens.

144
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,720
Everyone here is a respected elder.

145
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,760
You all know the art of reading people.

146
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,520
To understand is to question the heart,

147
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,680
the action,

148
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:49,800
not the origin.

149
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,200
I've never been

150
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,320
anyone's shadow.

151
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,160
If I didn't do it,

152
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,320
I won't take the blame.

153
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,400
I'm here today to visit you,

154
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,800
not to stir up trouble.

155
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,480
Sorry for any trouble caused.

156
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:24,080
I hope this doesn't affect

157
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,360
your ties.

158
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:30,840
Jiadi,

159
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,800
blood is thicker than water.

160
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,320
Don't make your grandpa choose sides.

161
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,320
If it's going nowhere,

162
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,000
I don't want to even start.

163
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,560
I don't want to get hurt,

164
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,800
or lose anything again.

165
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,760
Then promise me something too.

166
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,360
If one day,

167
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,960
I ask for your name,

168
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,560
your family, your past,

169
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,680
you have to tell me.

170
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,320
Because by then,

171
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,680
I'm ready

172
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,240
to step into your world.

173
00:11:58,560 --> 00:11:59,440
Just two things.

174
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,760
The Zhao family name
came from my grandpa.

175
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:06,000
I can't give it back to you.

176
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:08,920
From here on out,

177
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,080
you do you,

178
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,040
and I'll do me.

179
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,360
I dreamed we'd go hiking together.

180
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,040
It started out in daylight.

181
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:23,920
We kept walking and it got dark.

182
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,440
Then, all of a sudden, you vanished.

183
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,160
I can't figure it out.

184
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,200
Why would we

185
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,840
turn down an entrepreneur

186
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,520
who wants real change?

187
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,800
A favor,

188
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,520
or a friend.

189
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,520
You matter more than the favor.

190
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,480
There's so much I want to ask you.

191
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,040
Are you ready for this?

192
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,080
Mr. Zhao,

193
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,360
you can't stay here anymore.

194
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,320
Please leave.

195
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,280
You're something else.

196
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:21,480
"Don't worry about future hardships.

197
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:23,840
If your goal is the horizon,

198
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,200
then all the world sees is your back."

199
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,280
"Stand up,

200
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,120
and hold your head high again.

201
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,080
This is what real life looks like."

202
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,520
"The more it reaches for the light,

203
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:42,400
the deeper its roots grow underground,

204
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:43,800
stretching into darkness."

205
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:48,000
"Give every mountain,

206
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,920
and every river,

207
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:52,440
a name that feels warm."

208
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,400
"Hope you have a bright future ahead."

209
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:59,280
"If once together
with the wind the roc could rise,

210
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,560
he would fly ninety thousand miles
up to the skies."

211
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,200
"Sky makes the shore for boundless sea,

212
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,560
of mountain summits, I am the peak"

213
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,160
"My fur coat
worth a thousand coins of gold,

214
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,440
my flower-dappled horse
may be sold.

215
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,360
To buy good wine

216
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,360
that we may drown the woes age-old."

217
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,360
"I did have a lofty ideal when young,

218
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,600
and promised to rank first
in the world of man."

219
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,760
"More than glimmers,

220
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,600
beacons blaze solar might.

221
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,520
Continents away,

222
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,400
the cosmos ignites."

223
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,280
How many times have I told you?

224
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,080
Stop sighing in front of me.

225
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,840
Why can't you remember that?

226
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,560
It brings financial misfortune.

227
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:15,520
Boss.

228
00:16:15,520 --> 00:16:17,960
You have to use bait to fish.

229
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,440
Didn't I put bait on?

230
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,040
How could I not?

231
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:26,120
Look, something's biting already.

232
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:26,800
Wait, no.

233
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,240
Is that really a catch?

234
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,920
What even is this thing?

235
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,360
Boss.

236
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,120
We've been in Hang City for weeks.

237
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,120
We haven't done anything yet.

238
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,480
