241
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:50,880
Why are you in such a rush?

242
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,760
You think just talking will work?

243
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:58,440
Things aren't that simple face-to-face.

244
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,120
Hang City is tricky,

245
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:03,440
way more than you think.

246
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:13,320
Hello?

247
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:26,560
Got it.

248
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:35,680
[Li Residence]

249
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:55,560
Yan,

250
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,040
get her more.

251
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,720
I've begged already,

252
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:01,560
and I've cried too,

253
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:02,600
but you just won't listen.

254
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:04,240
What do you want from me?

255
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,080
Didn't I say already?

256
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:07,920
Let's just move on from this.

257
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,800
I'm not asking for your opinion.

258
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,800
Give my phone back.

259
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,480
Let me out.

260
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,320
Do you even realize

261
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:17,320
unlawful detention

262
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:18,320
is a real crime?

263
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:20,000
So I broke the law.

264
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:23,280
I just don't get it.

265
00:18:23,360 --> 00:18:24,680
How did you end up like this?

266
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:26,120
You weren't like this before.

267
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,000
He's the one I care about.

268
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:32,000
Why do you treat him this way?

269
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,560
Do you really know him?

270
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:36,760
Do you know what he's like?

271
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,640
Just because of his background,

272
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,760
you've already judged him.

273
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,360
Is that right?

274
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,080
Who his father is

275
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,800
doesn't matter at all.

276
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:53,960
Your generation's grudge

277
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:55,800
probably began

278
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,560
long before Jiadi was born.

279
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,520
Yeah, he wasn't born yet.

280
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,840
Hai's father

281
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,480
died because of Zhao Xin.

282
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,560
So tell me,

283
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:13,560
how could I let him into the Li family?

