Things are tense lately,

290
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:54,520
so we'll close the casino for now.

291
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,760
Keep your eyes open.

292
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,160
Got it. Don't worry.

293
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:01,960
Tonight, follow the car.

294
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,400
Okay.

295
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,680
Zhang Dongfeng,

296
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,720
or are you that Xiong...

297
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,520
No, that's not right.

298
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,920
Now it's Mr. Jiao.

299
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,520
Uncle.

300
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,400
Morning.

301
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:55,920
Come on.

302
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:56,880
Change your shoes.

303
00:21:57,080 --> 00:21:57,880
Go wash up.

304
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:13,560
You've worked all night.

305
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,360
Why not take a break?

306
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:15,040
It's alright.

307
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:21,000
Why are you just standing there?

308
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,280
Go to the bedroom.

309
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,040
Bring out the dirty clothes.

310
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:23,600
I'll do the laundry.

311
00:22:32,600 --> 00:22:33,760
You're messy every single day.

312
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:35,160
That underwear is ripped.

313
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,960
I threw it out for you, okay?

314
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:01,640
Put the gloves over there.

315
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:06,760
Uncle, maybe you should rest first.

316
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:07,760
Let's go grab a bite.

317
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:10,000
No need, you go ahead.

318
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:11,480
I'm not hungry.

319
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:12,720
I'll tidy up the bedroom.

320
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:18,320
Who is it? I'm coming!

321
00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:31,640
Ms. Cai.

322
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:40,360
Jiadi.

323
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,080
Ms. Cai.

324
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,000
Change and come out with me for a walk.

325
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,320
I don't feel like going out.

326
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,840
Don't make me drag you out.

327
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:15,000
[J. Equi Club]

328
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,720
I feel much better
after sweating it out.

329
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,400
Thanks, Ms. Cai.

330
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:56,080
What are your plans next?

331
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,400
I'll just start over.

332
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:07,480
It won't come to that.

333
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,320
You've built your name in Hang City.

334
00:25:10,520 --> 00:25:12,040
Even if you change direction,

335
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,480
you won't be starting from scratch.

336
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:16,280
I actually wanted to start a business.

337
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:19,160
Private equity is all about connections.

338
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:22,480
Now things are tense with the Lis.

339
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,040
Doing business

340
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:26,400
requires

341
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,960
connections.

342
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,200
Everyone is leveraging something.

343
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:32,520
The best uses the times
to their advantage,

344
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,240
and others rely on the right people.

345
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,040
I wanted to invest in you, to help you,

346
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,720
because you have qualities

347
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,560
that are hard to find.

348
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,080
First, you have a conscience,

349
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,320
and second, you're composed.

350
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,120
I've been in business for years,

351
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:52,320
seen all kinds of ups and downs.

352
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,120
The more I see,

353
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,000
the more I realize
how evil people can be.

354
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:00,560
Jiadi,

355
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,400
you can't make it in Hang City.

356
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,280
Come to Hai City.

357
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:14,360
Before I came to Hang City,
I had one goal,

358
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,600
to help Ke get the mine back.

359
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,920
But now I have one more.

360
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,560
I've found someone I care about here,

361
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:27,000
so I can't just leave.

362
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:30,040
No matter how hard it gets,

363
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,680
I'll grit my teeth and push through.

364
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:36,000
I can't explain why.

365
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:37,880
It's just a feeling.

366
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:41,440
If I take even half a step back here,

367
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:43,920
I might never get back again.

368
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:46,000
I get that,

369
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:48,640
but I don't agree.

370
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:53,840
What about you?

371
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,800
How's your dispute with the Chen family?

372
00:26:56,560 --> 00:26:57,760
I've been looking into it all along.

373
00:26:58,480 --> 00:27:00,320
And also Mr. Jiao,
the one we saw last time.

374
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,600
There are quite a few leads now,

375
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:06,520
but nothing obvious yet.

376
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:09,240
It's really not simple.

377
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:22,840
Huang Ruiyang?

378
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,080
This wine of yours is good.

379
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:26,360
The color already looks great,

380
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:31,800
and it smells pretty authentic.

381
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:37,640
Go on.

382
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:43,320
We met back up north before.

383
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:46,160
Let's just say,

384
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:48,000
I owe him a favor.

385
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,840
He wants to use me to meet you.

386
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,440
How much does he know about you?

387
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,240
Like the underground casino,

388
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:00,320
he hasn't found out, right?

389
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,920
No way.

390
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,160
It's well hidden.

391
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:10,080
Sharing the mining rights info

392
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,320
with Zhao Xin

393
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,760
was actually a risky move.

394
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,840
Lately,

395
00:28:15,840 --> 00:28:17,200
I can't afford any mistakes.

396
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,960
Shut down your underground casino

397
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:20,720
for now.

398
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,840
Don't let it interfere.

399
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,520
It's already closed.

400
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:32,440
So this time,

401
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:34,840
the commander-in-chief thing

402
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:35,680
can be considered done, right?

403
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:48,080
We're putting Zhao Jiadi out front

404
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,120
as a shield this time.

405
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:51,480
It's just a way to buy some time.

406
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,920
In the end, it's up to Mr. Li.

407
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,600
You know how it is.

408
00:28:58,800 --> 00:28:59,600
So,

409
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:03,120
Fan... Fan Longquan...

410
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,240
Fan Longquan just won't let go.

411
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:13,160
I heard he's been digging around

412
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,640
the mining site nonstop.

413
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:18,080
That guy,

414
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:19,040
seriously...

415
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:26,640
Huang Ruiyang...

416
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:28,240
Are we still meeting him?

417
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:31,160
Sure.

418
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:34,000
I know he's close with Zhao Xin,

419
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,880
but let him wait a bit first.

420
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:41,200
Some people just want a seat
at the big table.

421
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:47,560
It's not that simple.

422
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:35,920
Fan.

423
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:38,040
Need your signature here.

424
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:41,400
News from the mining site again.

425
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:42,320
We've found

426
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,200
the suppliers.

427
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:44,120
But,

428
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:45,720
they won't share the accounts with us.

429
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,760
I think we should

430
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,880
try something else.

431
00:30:52,040 --> 00:30:53,600
We can't count on them anyway.

432
00:30:57,520 --> 00:30:58,480
I brought in someone new

433
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,440
and told him to handle it
in a different way.

434
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:03,920
By the way,

435
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:07,160
keep an eye on the company's packages.

436
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:11,120
If anything comes from the mining site,

437
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,200
bring it straight to me.

438
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:18,880
Fan, you seem off lately.

439
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:21,040
Is it because of

440
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:22,040
Zhao Jiadi?

441
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,080
You should get back to work.

442
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:31,360
Alright.

443
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,400
Let me just say one last thing.

444
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,680
I think that young man

445
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:39,440
is actually decent.

446
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:52,600
Lan.

447
00:31:57,080 --> 00:32:01,600
[Shen Yulan, Fan Longquan's wife]

448
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:16,960
Fan.

449
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,320
What brings you here?

450
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:24,120
I was passing by after shopping.

451
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,480
Thought I'd drop in.

452
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:28,400
Where's Hu?

453
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:29,840
Mom's looking after him.

454
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,800
I made a lunchbox for Hu

455
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:36,040
and brought one for you too.

456
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,960
Good thing Zhu left earlier.

457
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,160
Otherwise, if he'd seen this,

458
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,920
he would have teased me.

459
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,400
No way, come on.

460
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,520
They've been with you for years.

461
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,600
Can't they tell

462
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:09,040
you've always been a kid

463
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:11,840
at heart?

464
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:20,200
Only you can tell.

465
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:29,080
Last night, you thought I was asleep,

466
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:32,160
and you sat on the sofa all night.

467
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,800
Wasn't that exhausting?

468
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:39,440
Not really.

469
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:53,080
Come here, let me massage you.

470
00:34:08,200 --> 00:34:10,480
Fan,

471
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:12,200
you really can't hide your temper.

472
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,600
If you were mad,

473
00:34:15,600 --> 00:34:16,840
he would've exploded already.

474
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,840
The reason you couldn't sleep

475
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,520
was probably guilt, right?

476
00:34:27,560 --> 00:34:28,560
Let me take a guess.

477
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:36,760
Is it about

478
00:34:36,760 --> 00:34:38,800
that genius kid

479
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:39,920
you mentioned before?

480
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:49,080
What's done is done.

481
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,600
What's the point

482
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:53,840
of saying all this?

483
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:58,000
At first, I was really mad,

484
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:01,920
but after thinking it through,

485
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,760
I realized I'm not good at much.

486
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,680
But as for reading people,

487
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,760
I've never misjudged anyone.

488
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,280
It's just that back then,

489
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:18,320
I shouldn't have reacted that way.

490
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:19,720
So?

491
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,800
There's just too much
mixed up in all this.

492
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:25,160
It's impossible to sort it all out,

493
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,520
and no matter how much I regret it,

494
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:34,240
I guess that's just how it is.

495
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:35,480
How could it be?

496
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:38,320
Things might stay tangled,

497
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,880
but your heart won't.

498
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:44,880
He's been through so much.

499
00:35:45,200 --> 00:35:46,280
Imagine how much that hurts.

500
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:49,320
He needs to know

501
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,440
what you're thinking right now.

502
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,840
Even if you part ways,

503
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,360
you should leave on good terms.

504
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,600
Wang.

505
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:22,040
About Zhao Jiadi,

506
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,000
what's your decision?

507
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,360
I gave him

508
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,160
a few days off.

509
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:29,960
Just a heads-up for you,

510
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:31,880
Zhao Jiadi

511
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:32,760
is a hot potato now.

512
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:40,840
Han Xuedong, to be honest,

513
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:42,760
I used to find you annoying.

514
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:45,240
But now I feel like

515
00:36:46,240 --> 00:36:47,840
you're getting a bit shameless.

516
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:55,120
Zhao Jiadi is with Risheng.

517
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:56,990
Even if the Li family has the reach,

518
00:36:56,990 --> 00:36:58,320
they can't touch here.

519
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:04,160
Wang Qihan, what do you take me for?

520
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,520
No matter how cold I seem,

521
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:07,960
I have to protect Zhao
for the sake of profit.

522
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:09,760
With Jufeng here,

523
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,720
Zhao Jiadi is our money-maker.

524
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:14,400
I'm just worried about you,

525
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,920
messing up things with Mr. Li.

526
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:16,800
I'm just giving you a heads-up.

527
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:22,120
What's so funny?

528
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:23,280
Hurry up and apologize to me.

529
00:37:25,200 --> 00:37:26,560
You really have no shame.

530
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,360
After all these years as friends,

531
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,600
don't act like

532
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,360
you don't care.

533
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:35,600
I'm still a shareholder here.

534
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,760
I'm one of the partners too.

535
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:38,720
Isn't that right?

536
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:40,560
At least show me some respect.

537
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:42,680
I'm here to discuss business today,

538
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:44,200
not to beg you for anything.

539
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:20,400
Jiadi, you look tired.

540
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:24,000
Take a break. I'll handle the rest.

541
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:25,560
No rush at all.

542
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:26,680
I'm not tired.

543
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:31,240
Sweating a bit actually wakes me up.

544
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,280
It's great having a courtyard like this.

545
00:38:36,520 --> 00:38:37,920
You can plant whatever you want here.

546
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,320
Maybe raise some small animals later.

547
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,640
I picked the tea leaves

548
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,200
on the back hill.

549
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:49,920
Try some.

550
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:52,440
Alright.

551
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:01,720
That's good tea.

552
00:39:03,080 --> 00:39:04,080
Mr. Huang,

553
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:05,240
what kind of seeds are those?

554
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:07,720
Oh, these? Radish seeds.

555
00:39:08,640 --> 00:39:09,800
They can be planted
in fall and winter.

556
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:13,960
Fall and winter radishes
are even more valuable.

557
00:39:15,720 --> 00:39:17,000
The extra touch of frost

558
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,240
helps radishes grow.

559
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,400
That's why older folks always say,

560
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:23,440
"frost-touched radishes
are as precious as ginseng."

561
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,880
People say talent is worth gold.

562
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,520
But for radish,

563
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,320
life is just too unpredictable.

564
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:37,800
Fate has other plans.

565
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,920
When I was in my teens,

566
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:47,920
I joined the Boatmen's Guild
as a boatman.

567
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,160
Once you're on the boat,

568
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,480
your life belongs to the sea.

569
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:54,840
If you die,

570
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:56,920
that's just how it goes.

571
00:39:58,040 --> 00:39:59,440
If you make it, it's another year.

572
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:01,800
I did that for six years,

573
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:04,040
saved every bit I could,

574
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,920
and bought my very first boat.

575
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:09,920
It was small and barely held together.

